  <launchable type="desktop-id">me.iepure.devtoolbox.desktop</launchable>
  <name>Dev Toolbox</name>
  <summary>Development tools at your fingertips</summary>
  <developer_name translatable="no">Alessandro Iepure</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>If you're tired of endlessly looking online for the right tool, or to
      find again that website of which you don't recall the name just for a quick
      conversion, this is the right app for you.</p>

    <p>This is a collection of powerful yet simple-to-use tools and utilities
      to solve the most common daily development problems.</p>

    <p>Includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>JSON to YAML converter and vice-versa</li>
      <li>CRON expressions parser</li>
      <li>GZip compressor and decompressor</li>
      <li>Formatters for common programming languages</li>
      <li>Hash generators</li>
      <li>Regex tester</li>
      <li>Markdown Previewer</li>
      <li>Image converters</li>
      <li>Much more...</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
